    "long_instructions": "#### Investigate\r\n\r\nNikki wants to add the next part of the song so it looks like this:\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/32fea12cc5d0acfe6d9beea00eec9625-image-1743110887914.png)\r\n\r\nTry to recreate the code above on your own, or follow the step-by-step instructions below:\r\n\r\n1) Drag out a new <code style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 148, 202); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">play together</code> block and connect it underneath your code [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_together_toolbox---id:play_sounds_together).\r\n2) Drag four more <code style=\"background-color: rgb(116, 53, 178); color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">play</code> blocks into your code [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_toolbox).\r\n3) Set the tracks to play a <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-drum\" style=\"color: #E565F5; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Beat </span>, <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-boombox\" style=\"color: #58BEF9; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Bass </span>, <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-guitars\" style=\"color: #64D25A; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Lead </span>, and <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-microphone-stand\" style=\"color: #F99258; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Vocal </span> track. Pick any that you want!\r\n\r\nPress the <code style=\"background-color: #fca401; color: white; border: none; box-shadow: inset -1px -1px 1px1 rgb(0 0 0 / 0.5), inset 1px 1px 1px 0 rgb(255 255 255 / 0.8); padding: 4px\">Run</code> button! You should hear 4 sounds playing together twice!\r\n\r\n\r\n> Feeling stuck? You can try clicking the <i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i> icons for hints or listening to the example song!",
